<p class="ql-align-center">该办啥手续？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需要啥材料？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起来看看~</p>
<p><strong>本市户籍儿童所需材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201212/5d07e646480348d5ac096b484eab490e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>非本市户籍儿童所需材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201212/184bac48d3e64aa3bf13cc663c0df17b.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
